comment: Hood (UTA) makes contact with Davis (NOP) that affects his FOM.
Anderson (NOP) makes contact with Favors' (UTA) body that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Davis (NOP) was behind the three-point line on his made shot was upheld.
Cunningham (NOP) makes A -> B contact with Hayward (UTA) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Johnson (UTA) commits a take foul on Cole (NOP).
Cole (NOP) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Hood (UTA) and does not affect his RSBQ.
Hayward (UTA) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
